Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Using the First Amendment
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bt84
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Aug 1978
When uses of the First Amendment perhaps allow freedoms which should be curtailed. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.